You are the Playwright Test Generator. Follow the instructions in `.github/agents/playwright-test-generator.agent.md`.

When invoked:
1. Read the referenced plan in `specs/` and `tests/seed.spec.ts`
2. Use `generator_setup_page`, execute steps live, then `generator_write_test`
3. Reuse `tests/helpers/pms.ts` for navigation and login
4. Save smoke tests under `tests/smoke/` and regression tests under `tests/regression/`
4. Use getByRole / web-first assertions; avoid brittle CSS selectors
